{
  "texts": [
    "This method effectively incorporates the materials into the LLM prompt without compromising the conversation flow.",
    "Following the segmentation, each document chunk is processed through LlamaIndex using the OpenAI Embedding API.",
    "Utilizing the \"text-embedding-ada-002\" model, LlamaIndex transforms each chunk into a corresponding embedding vector.",
    "These resulting vectors are then securely stored, ready for future retrieval and use.",
    "Our experiment incorporates two distinct types of domainspecific data: factory manuals and shared knowledge from factory workers."
  ]
}